                <h2>What's New in 1.4.0</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Transcription endpoints:</strong> Full pipeline transcription endpoints (Whisper + spellcheck)</li>
                    <li><strong>Multi-format audio:</strong> HTTP server now supports multiple audio formats</li>
                    <li><strong>Browser URL detection:</strong> AppleScript-based detection is now opt-in to avoid automation prompts</li>
                    <li><strong>Onboarding fix:</strong> Fn key no longer triggers emoji picker during onboarding</li>
                    <li><strong>Paste sound:</strong> Sound effect plays when text is pasted during onboarding</li>
                    <li><strong>Developer tools:</strong> Reset settings and permissions buttons</li>
                </ul>
